1. Čuvajte (*čuvajte*) svoje zdravlje. (Take care of (*literally*: Guard) your health.)
2. *Čuvaj* ovo mesto dok se ne vratim. (Guard this place until I come back.)
3. Nemoj da mi *čuvaš* mesto, doći ću na vreme. (Don't save a seat for me, I'll come on time.)
4. *Čuvajući* svoju privatnost, nije želela da odgovori na pitanja novinara. (Guarding (*literally*: Keeping) her privacy, she didn't want to answer the journalist's questions.)
5. Treba *čuvati* prirodu od zagađenja. (We need to protect (*literally*: Guard) nature from pollution.)
6. Molim vas, *čuvajte* red u redu za kupovinu. (Please, maintain (*literally*: Guard) the order in the line for shopping.)
7. Policija *čuva* red tokom demonstracija. (Police are maintaining (*literally*: Guarding) order during the protests.)
8. *Čuvajte* se pasa u parku, neki mogu biti agresivni. (Beware of (*literally*: Guard yourselves from) dogs in the park, some can be aggressive.)
9. Oni *čuvaju* svoju decu od loših uticaja društva. (They are protecting (*literally*: Guarding) their children from bad influences of society.)
10. Zabranjeno je *čuvati* pse na ovom trgu. (It is forbidden to keep (*literally*: Guard) dogs in this square.)